  "keyFeatures": [
    "Physics-based lithium-ion battery models (SPM, SPMe, DFN, MPM, MSMR)",
    "Lead-acid and sodium-ion battery model support",
    "Equivalent circuit models (Thevenin, ECM)",
    "Flexible experiment definition with CC, CV, and rest steps",
    "Multiple solvers: CasADi, IDAKLU, SciPy, JAX",
    "Rich parameter sets from published literature (Chen2020, Marquis2019, OKane2022, etc.)",
    "Built-in plotting and visualization tools",
    "BatchStudy for parameter sweeps and sensitivity analysis",
    "Extensible submodel architecture for custom physics",
    "Support for 1D, 2D and 3D spatial discretisations"
  ],
